{
  "texts": [
    "A study of Tao et al (2022) proposed an early warning system for predicting student's academic performance using DNNs.",
    "The study aimed to predict student's future course grades using their prior learning experiences and then utilized clustering algorithms to find instances of comparable learning experiences, to help students perform better academically.",
    "The DNNs method was integrated with a grade prediction and learning recommendation model.",
    "The results showed that the proposed model can fit the data more accurately and improve the prediction accuracy when compared with LR, RF, and BP Neural Networks.",
    "All reviewed studies that used CNN techniques are summarized in Table 3."
  ]
}